Package com.codeski.nbt.tags

Class NBT

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.codeski.nbt.tags.NBT
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    NBTByte, NBTByteArray, NBTCompound, NBTDouble, NBTEnd, NBTFloat, NBTInteger, NBTIntegerArray, NBTList, NBTLong, NBTShort, NBTString
    public abstract class NBT
extends java.lang.Object
    Base abstract class that all subclasses extend upon. More information can be found at the article for NBT format on Minecraft Wiki:
    http://minecraft.gamepedia.com/NBT_format
